                                determined under paragraph (c)(1)(iv)
                                of this section, for any hour in which
                                the parameters under paragraph
                                (c)(1)(iv)(A) of this section do not show
                                that the NO<sub>x</sub> emission controls are operating
                                properly, use the NO<sub>x</sub> emission
                                rate from Table LM–2 of this section
                                for the fuel combusted during the hour
                                with the highest NO<sub>x</sub> emission rate.
