                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>EF<sub>NOx</sub></td>
                                        <td>
                                            = Either the NOX emission factor from
                                            Table LM–2 of this section or the fuel- and
                                            unit-specific NOX emission rate determined
                                            under paragraph (c)(1)(iv) of this section
                                            (lb/mmBtu).
                                        </td>
