                                fuel is combusted in the hour, use the
                                highest emission factor for all of the
                                fuels combusted in the hour. If records
                                are missing as to which fuel was combusted
                                in the hour, use the highest
                                emission factor for all of the fuels capable
                                of being combusted in the unit.
