                                        the procedures used to document
                                        proper operation of the NO<sub>x</sub> emission
                                        controls. The plan shall include the parameters
                                        monitored (e.g., water-to-fuel
                                        ratio) and the acceptable ranges for
                                        each parameter used to determine
                                        proper operation of the unit’s NO<sub>x</sub> controls.
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        For unmanned facilities, the
                                        records required by paragraphs (e)(1),
                                        (e)(2) and (e)(4) of this section may be
                                        kept at a central location, rather than
                                        at the facility.
                                    </li>
